SERVER.md

# ── Large media ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Audio and box art are served from the PocketBase backend, which is the
# source of truth. Keeping ~700 MB of binaries out of git keeps clones fast.
# Re-populate the server with backend/migrate_content.py and
# backend/upload_game_art.py.
assets/sound/music/
assets/images/games/
DevCDN/audio
DevCDN/art

